{"tid":2296584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"做香港人 慘過狗 日日比人虐待 摧殘 折磨","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:35:46.000Z","uid":123264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"893db87c9e89739cdc562b33e153af1f6b29674a","tid":2296584,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"香港人就係原罪 同維吾爾人一樣 只要係呢個民族就會被逼慢性自殺 一生係血汗工廠做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班五毛藍絲波台狗 咪成日用豬仔笑恥笑手足同抗爭運動既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢班人係香港淪陷之後都係要入集中營 無人會例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時係個camp到諗起係連登恥笑抗爭運動既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到老婆仔女比人強姦 個心入面 佢地會諗 :<br />\nWell...至少我地恥笑過連登仔....都係值得既...豬仔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef137559f820f4232d849466553e144c785cc9ca","tid":2296584,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x3"},{"pid":"5f4a7ec1a50f89230ebe964b9704e5d5f99d4f04","tid":2296584,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7fe4916cc5a74892353d05f9b2a8ead5e67413","tid":2296584,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f4a7ec1a50f89230ebe964b9704e5d5f99d4f04","tid":2296584,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac